	 program per part (Boolean) -  Output one program per part

 Use 
	 part len as prog len (Boolean) -  Use parts length as program 
	 length rather than edge against the fence. Without this set 
	 L & Rs length = part width 
 Display 
	 RPM (Boolean) -  Display RPM (Spindle Speed) in output. Without 
	 this, the spindle speed is set to 0 
 Display 
	 Operation Depth (Boolean) -  Display operation depth in output.
